Data-DPath

DPath is not XPath.

Originally started as XML::XPath fork, later decided to start from
scratch, by saving some ideas.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Data::DPath

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Data-DPath

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Data-DPath

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Data-DPath

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Data-DPath


